<view><view class="explain-rule"><view class="rule-title">说明：</view><view class="rule-text">1. 点击“全部绑定到当前账号”可以将礼品卡一次性绑定到当前账户；</view><view class="rule-text">2. 点击“绑定到当前账号”，可以只绑定当前的礼品卡；</view><view class="rule-text">3. 也可以复制“秘钥”，将秘钥转送给好友，好友可以通过绑定礼品卡功能，绑定到自己账号；</view></view><view class="binding"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['bindingAll',['$event']]]]]}}" class="binding-but" bindtap="__e">全部绑定到当前账号</view></view><view class="gift-card"><block wx:for="{{cardList}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><view class="gift-card-item"><view class="card-info"><view>卡号：</view><view>{{item.cardNumber}}</view></view><view class="card-info"><view>卡秘钥：</view><view><view>{{item.password}}</view></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['copyCode',['$0'],[[['cardList','',index]]]]]]]}}" class="copy-key" bindtap="__e">复制</view></view><view class="card-info"><view>有效期：</view><view>{{item.beginTime+" - "+item.endTime}}</view></view><view class="binding-key"><block wx:if="{{item.status=='1'}}"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['bindingOne',['$0'],[[['cardList','',index]]]]]]]}}" class="binding-key-but" bindtap="__e">绑定到当前账号</view></block><block wx:if="{{item.status=='2'}}"><view class="binding-key-but-dark">已绑定</view></block><block wx:if="{{item.status=='3'}}"><view class="binding-key-but-dark">已失效</view></block></view></view></block></view><view style="height:100rpx;"></view></view>